The evidence with the title 'Feisal Abdul Rauf - Wikipedia ' says Feisal Abdul Rauf is a Kuwaiti American sufi imam, author, and activist whose stated goal is to improve relations between the Muslim world and the West . From 1983 to 2009 , he served as Imam of Masjid Al-Farah, a mosque in New York City. He has written three books on Islam and its place in contemporary Western  ... 
